markets.title: Will a bill enacting **paid parental leave** become law by the end of March?
markets.subtitle: By March 31, 2022
markets.rules_primary: If a bill enacting paid parental leave becomes law between Issuance and March 31, 2022, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
All market participants should familiarize themselves with these legally binding rules before trading on the market.

The Expiration Date of the Contract shall be the sooner of the first 10:00 AM following the occurrence of an event  represented at the Underlying that is encompassed in the Payout Criterion (i.e. a bill enacting paid parental leave becoming law reported by Congress.gov), the first 10:00 AM following the release of the data (Congress.gov updates) for March 31, 2022, and April 07, 2022.
